{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_06_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 みんなが支えてくれてる",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影初日終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the first day of shooting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……今日は本当に\n本っっっ当に！　すみませんでした！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san… Today was really…\nReally! I'm so sorry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "任せて下さいって言ったのに緊張しっぱなしで\n結局{user}さんに来てもらって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I said to leave it to me‚ I was nervous the whole time.\nIn the end‚ I made trouble for you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 17.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "現場の人達にもいっぱい迷惑を掛けて\n最後は一緒に謝ってもらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and for everyone on set.\nAnd we ended up apologizing together…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 24.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ。でも次は気を付けようか\n緊張してたり不安なら、もっと早めに言うんだぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay. But next time‚ be more careful‚ alright?\nIf you're nervous or unsure‚ just tell me sooner.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 32.156414636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "私……迷惑、掛けたくなかったんです\nただでさえ、{user}さんは忙しいですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… I didn't want to cause trouble.\nEspecially since you're always so busy‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.756414636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "いつまでも甘えてばかりじゃダメだって……\nソロの仕事も、一人で立派にやり遂げなきゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't keep relying on you forever.\nI have to be able to handle solo work on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2897479694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 47.3897479694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、ライブの告知もしないとですし\nLizNoirのためにも頑張らなきゃって……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ we need to promote the live shows.\nI have to do my best for LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8230813027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 53.9230813027
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、頑張ろうとすればするほど空回りしちゃって\n私……結局ダメダメでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the harder I try‚ the more I seem to mess up.\nI… I ended up being a total failure…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.056414636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの評判だって落としかねない\nそういう振る舞いだったと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might have even tarnished\nLizNoir's reputation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8230813027,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.4897479694
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "私、どうしたら挽回出来るでしょう……\nこのままじゃ本当に、LizNoir失格です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can I make it up…?\nAt this rate‚ I'll truly be disqualified from LizNoir…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.756414636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、あんまり一人で気負い過ぎないことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ don't put too much pressure on yourself alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.656414636,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.2480243207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……\nリズノワの一人として頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but…\nas a member of LizNoir‚ I have to give it my all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.381357654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirは一人じゃないだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir isn't just you‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0480243207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 88.4538059474
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　それは、もちろん\n莉央さん、葵さん、こころ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Of course!\nRio-san‚ Aoi-san‚ Kokoro-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7871392807,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "そして私の四人でLizNoirです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And me‚ the four of us together make up LizNoir.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7538059474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.8204726141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "愛はLizNoirを代表して、とか\n『背負って』いる気でいるのかもしれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might feel like you're 'carrying' LizNoir\nas its representative‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "『支えられて』もいる、って思うんだ\n背中にはその三人と、俺もついてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but remember‚ you're also being 'supported'.\nYou've got those three and me right behind you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0999956767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 109.7762736243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが背中を、支えてくれている……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone has been supporting me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7762736243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "離れていても、莉央さんも、葵さんも、こころも\n{user}さんまでついてくれてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when we're apart‚ Rio-san‚ Aoi-san‚ and Kokoro-chan…\nEven {user}-san is here for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.042950972,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.7762832881
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "私が一人で参加する仕事でも\nみんなでやってきた経験が私を助けてくれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even in jobs where I participate alone…\nThe experiences we've had together always help me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1762832881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "私にはみんなと積み重ねてきた経験があるから\n今回のオファーがきたんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I have the experiences I've built up with everyone‚\nso this offer came to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.7429275752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 137.2095942419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\n私、今度こそ大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san.\nI'll be okay this time for real.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3095942419,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、いい顔になった\n……じゃあ、今日はもうゆっくり休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you're looking better.\n…Well then‚ take a good rest for today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.7333122253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.7083283982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "気付いてないかもしれないけど\n今日の靴、左右で違うぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You might not have noticed‚ but…\nYour shoes today are different on the left and right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8666516621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-night",
      "startTime": 153.7735210977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_06_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "……！？　きゃーー！？\n私、今日この靴でスタジオに行ったんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…!? Kyaa!?\nDid I really go to the studio in these shoes today!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.5735210977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
